{"tid":2241371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東打工仔紀實:在廣東辭職回家第五天了，今天去戶外挖竹筍回家做菜吃","createTime":"2020-10-13T09:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T11:30:32.000Z","uid":26770,"like":178,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"08957ea62c2a7883759171eb490b6d60404405be","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2gHq_ZMJZrs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2gHq_ZMJZrs&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=1ab63825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2gHq_ZMJZrs</a><br />\n<br />\n成堆中國佬安慰自己開心最緊要<br />\n當日出省城打工就係因為搵到錢, 現在係工業商業全死無得唔走<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n女人仲慘, 成堆女人要比男人騎<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hQfRfHilPG4?t=119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhQfRfHilPG4%3Ft%3D119&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b10f8241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hQfRfHilPG4?t=119</a><br />\n<br />\n現在成堆中國後生女做雞,呢堆女人白坐成日唔會有生意"},{"pid":"1a10f3139ca7b4455216062bed03c7c25a11de30","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":76,"dislike":4,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:10.000Z","msg":"成堆地改左去起樓, 商場,停車場<br />\n<br />\n挖竹筍頂唔到好多人, 現在工廠唔係一間間摺,係全個工廠園陣亡<br />\n好快要食觀音土"},{"pid":"9a11e405a9ae90f5ec85eee2a58bc33581afba7e","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4129555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheme.udn.com%2Ftheme%2Fstory%2F6775%2F4129555&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a67e80a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4129555</a><br />\n<br />\n'食土饃真正來源雖不可考，但是土饃大會新聞一出，有網民回憶說，曾看過一齣電視劇，在鬧飢荒的年代沒吃的，最後吃觀音土，因不能消化，最後肚子脹死。在尚未發達的年代，大陸大多為務農的農民，需看天吃飯，遇上鬧飢荒時，觀音土就成為吃完樹皮、草根後果腹對象，「大躍進」後演變成大飢荒，觀音土也扮演相同角色。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">觀音土因食起味道有些糯米味，因此又叫做糯米土，是白泥巴，有的地方稱之為「仙泥」</span>，顆粒細膩。據悉，食用觀音土的做法簡單，可以做成泥丸子，放點鹽用水加熱，食起像糯米元宵。人吃了觀音土會有飽腹感，儘管能夠<strong>抑止住飢餓</strong>，但若大量食用，人體<strong>無法消化它、也無法排洩</strong>，只得<span class=\"x-large\">用竹籤、樹枝、手指掏，令食者十分痛苦，最後會腸胃潰爛而死</span>。'"},{"pid":"ac3c8cc0686093f22afb223cb94d5c08647fadd2","tid":2241371,"uid":47462,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"支那自己整個病毒攬炒全球仲玩死埋自己經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0728553f47e94754e69e38fa076918d958fbd87","tid":2241371,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"現代中國革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6e34ee248be29f606b3555c10acb01952f1d99","tid":2241371,"uid":299514,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"啱㗎勒！餓撚死你哋班死支那就啱勒！<br />\n你做雞都無人屌你呀！"},{"pid":"da5c4e6fa86aada475aa2bd7008aff756b0e6792","tid":2241371,"uid":55913,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:45:01.000Z","msg":"輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲d屎都無得食<br />\n仲搵兩隻五毛放負把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想放棄了 支竹"},{"pid":"2ba0667c883bce9b6d61a43d7160057b513304e9","tid":2241371,"uid":352926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:46:05.000Z","msg":"回鄉創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4beb501cee5a29508460c92f3c9c349a3c6b58","tid":2241371,"uid":11148,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"水退後女人可以靠閪生財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b756f58c6a33edbe358f31321c66f9b85f7a743","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f4beb501