"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d8f09facf446f08c2adf49c061cf0f1e77bb3b5","tid":2241371,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"好多雞供應"},{"pid":"d5eb41aeb7ce52a11a4859d788d4c77865ce2090","tid":2241371,"uid":247139,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ek97Cqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEk97Cqb.jpg&h=f1d4d640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721c207e3c1970297777616a062c03ec3fcb1121","tid":2241371,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:54:17.000Z","msg":"Ｄ雞多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac386d103588cb4379d0c140c61981079a90833","tid":2241371,"uid":137159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"我睇過依條友啲片，早排話三四皮人仔去做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔計三四皮可以做乜，我假設佢目標係搵二千人仔一個月，一年二萬四，即係佢生意年回報要超過五成，賣白粉就有可能"},{"pid":"44a1e3e8611ec035dcc741550471d5866c8beb2f","tid":2241371,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"They deserves<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍應該去中國陪韭菜食草<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459ea9e2351cfc03edc54338d51f2c7ca789ae75","tid":2241371,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac3c8cc0686093f22afb223cb94d5c08647fadd2","tid":2241371,"uid":47462,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"支那自己整個病毒攬炒全球仲玩死埋自己經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"業力果報。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d94325483daf30c6881fc7ecaba34dae25cb85c","tid":2241371,"uid":39277,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e3eaafc4da91bb4122863a327c82ce9aedf58a89","tid":2241371,"uid":121546,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"9a11e405a9ae90f5ec85eee2a58bc33581afba7e","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4129555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheme.udn.com%2Ftheme%2Fstory%2F6775%2F4129555&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a67e80a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4129555</a><br />\n<br />\n'食土饃真正來源雖不可考，但是土饃大會新聞一出，有網民回憶說，曾看過一齣電視劇，在鬧飢荒的年代沒吃的，最後吃觀音土，因不能消化，最後肚子脹死。在尚未發達的年代，大陸大多為務農的農民，需看天吃飯，遇上鬧飢荒時，觀音土就成為吃完樹皮、草根後果腹對象，「大躍進」後演變成大飢荒，觀音土也扮演相同角色。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">觀音土因食起味道有些糯米味，因此又叫做糯米土，是白泥巴，有的地方稱之為「仙泥」</span>，顆粒細膩。據悉，食用觀音土的做法簡單，可以做成泥丸子，放點鹽用水加熱，食起像糯米元宵。人吃了觀音土會有飽腹感，儘管能夠<strong>抑止住飢餓</strong>，但若大量食用，人體<strong>無法消化它、也無法排洩</strong>，只得<span class=\"x-large\">用竹籤、樹枝、手指掏，令食者十分痛苦，最後會腸胃潰爛而死</span>。'"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"正常人冇野食都係唔會食泥同樹皮既，係人都知依d野食左會死，多數係飢荒餓死既人都係前一日仲覺得自己應該捱得住，點知第2日就虛弱到落唔到床，然後慢慢等死<br />\n<br />\n大多數人就算餓死都唔會易子相食，寧願捱餓，有咁多人話自己做過係因為幸存者偏差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"大陸有啲省食樹皮好叻，識揀嚟食，樹皮唔係隻隻都食得<br />\n<br />\n依家學定野外求生，睇下依啲昆蟲同植物食得，遲啲打仗都唔會餓死"},{"pid":"7d2975f2cee8827e9bf0163f786859a9dfac64a3","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"2ac386d103588cb4379d0c140c61981079a90833","tid":2241371,"uid":137159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"我睇過依條友啲片，早排話三四皮人仔去做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔計三四皮可以做乜，我假設佢目標係搵二千人仔一個月，一年二萬四，即係佢生意年回報要超過五成，賣白粉就有可能"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"現在係連去深圳工行