id":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"2ac386d103588cb4379d0c140c61981079a90833","tid":2241371,"uid":137159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"我睇過依條友啲片，早排話三四皮人仔去做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔計三四皮可以做乜，我假設佢目標係搵二千人仔一個月，一年二萬四，即係佢生意年回報要超過五成，賣白粉就有可能"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"現在係連去深圳工行得最低級的打雜都要上床,買位<br />\n中共就人為製造李子柒現象<br />\n<br />\n賣唱可以變明星,村姑可以變知名主播<br />\n仲有工廠妹變歌星<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><ins>其實係獅子山下勵志故事+American Dream的高仿</ins><br />\n大把中國最低層SHORT左FF 自己成為下一個李子柒</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"個個發夢做網紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d865077d53a99e6c9ece4beb0089174bcac1c6cb","tid":2241371,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c3f7db8fe2d601b263553536c06cdc0504e6d5f","tid":2241371,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3f4beb501cee5a29508460c92f3c9c349a3c6b58","tid":2241371,"uid":11148,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"水退後女人可以靠閪生財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"男人可以賣菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:27:17.000Z","msg":"都要有人有錢買先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20da942ab1a5b553d9352ab69536ddbe979c50e5","tid":2241371,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"推多d 呢d 片 等佢地有樣學樣 到時係郊區打生打死"},{"pid":"5a9ff2bf34a8037be471c0eeaf4bb55ed981d837","tid":2241371,"uid":20867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1a10f3139ca7b4455216062bed03c7c25a11de30","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":76,"dislike":4,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:10.000Z","msg":"成堆地改左去起樓, 商場,停車場<br />\n<br />\n挖竹筍頂唔到好多人, 現在工廠唔係一間間摺,係全個工廠園陣亡<br />\n好快要食觀音土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:58:19.000Z","msg":"以為 觀音土 = 香爐灰<br />\n原來「是一種含鋁的矽酸鹽礦物」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">觀音土在大飢荒時期曾被飢民當成食物充飢，吃下暫時解除飢餓感。崇禎三年（1630年）陝西大飢，陝西巡按馬懋才在《備陳大飢疏》說陝西人民只能吃觀音土填飽肚子。中華人民共和國1960年代三年大飢荒期間也有不少人吃觀音土。\n\n但觀音土並非有機食物，含大量氧化鋁，不能被人體消化吸收，儘管吃了不會餓肚子，少量吃不致命，但由於毫無營養成份，吃久了人還是會死於營養不良。此外，吃了觀音土有會腹脹、手足浮腫、便秘等症狀。因為胃部的填充對飢餓感的減除只起到一小部分的作用，曾出現過大量食用觀音土致死的案例。</code></pre><br />\n~Wikipedia"},{"pid":"dee0c17b0c5a45fa6df0d16d7fb29cc4fdaa081b","tid":2241371,"uid":171389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:28:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"204bec3849259159e023910fb2e5d18addf5bf3c","tid":2241371,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c3f7db8fe2d601b263553536c06cdc0504e6d5f","tid":2241371,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3f4beb501cee5a29508460c92f3c9c349a3c6b58","tid":2241371,"uid":11148,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"水退後女人可以靠閪生財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"男人可以賣菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:36:38.000Z","msg":"可能五十蚊人仔都賣唔出一次"},{"pid":"d4efc06d973927618c7da0c51287dd5352009d70","tid":2241371,"uid":335924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:38:47.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"073421de54f524572bb9993d064bfb7be9c7b66f","tid":2241371,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:42:20.000Z","msg":"支那人又贏左個世界 做雞救地球"},{"pid":"a4220cdb6987ab9009b41c1e81348456e9b1bb0a","tid":2241371,"uid":411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"個個都想做華農兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a103bc570e0f564f1a04232314f5cfe328986116","tid":2241371,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08957ea62c2a7883759171eb490b6d60404405be","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2gHq_ZMJZrs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2gHq_ZMJZrs&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=1ab63825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2gHq_ZMJZrs</a><br />\n<br />\n成堆中國佬安慰自己開心最緊要<br />\n當日出省城打工就係因為搵到錢, 現在係工業商業全死無得唔走<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n女人仲慘, 成堆女人要比男人騎<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hQfRfHilPG4?t=119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhQfRfHilPG4%3Ft%3D119&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b10f8241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hQfRfHilPG4?t=119</a><br />\n<br />\n現在成堆中國後生女做雞,呢堆女人白坐成日唔會有生意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"疫情前都大一堆做雞啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩特別"},{"pid":"b63234de9e4f875ab69ffaf5253daae0f785c3ce","tid":2241371,"uid":101945,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"有錢男人包起一百個女人<br />\n女人再包返起窮男人<br />\n實現內循環"},{"pid":"4f1bba0ea57a5ceeb15b5c2fd7285c74b62d71fa","tid":2241371,"uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3eaafc4da91bb4122863a327c82ce9aedf58a89","tid":2241371,"uid":121546,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"9a11e405a9ae90f5ec85eee2a58bc33581afba7e","tid":2241371,"uid":26770,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4129555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheme.udn.com%2Ftheme%2Fstory%2F6775%2F4129555&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a67e80a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4129555</a><br />\n<br />\n'食土饃真正來源雖不可考，但是土饃大會新聞一出，有網民回憶說，曾看過一齣電視劇，在鬧飢荒的年代沒吃的，最後吃觀音土，因不能消化，最後肚子脹死。在尚未發達的年代，大陸大多為務農的農民，需看天吃飯，遇上鬧飢荒時，觀音土就成為吃完樹皮、草根後果腹對象，「大躍進」後演變成大飢荒，觀音土也扮演相同角色。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">觀音土因食起味道有些糯米味，因此又叫做糯米土，是白泥巴，有的地方稱之為「仙泥」</span>，顆粒細膩。據悉，食用觀音土的做法簡單，可以做成泥丸子，放點鹽用水加熱，食起像糯米元宵。人吃了觀音土會有飽腹感，儘管能夠<strong>抑止住飢餓</strong>，但若大量食用，人體<strong>無法消化它、也無法排洩</strong>，只得<span class=\"x-large\">用竹籤、樹枝、手指掏，令食者十分痛苦，最後會腸胃潰爛而死</span>。'"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"正常人冇野食都係唔會食泥同樹皮既，係人都知依d野食左會死，多數係飢荒餓死既人都係前一日仲覺得自己應該捱得住，點知第2日就虛弱到落唔到床，然後慢慢等死<br />\n<br />\n大多數人就算餓死都唔會易子相食，寧願捱餓，有咁多人話自己做過係因為幸存者偏差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"樹皮食入面果層<br />\n唔係外面硬果層啦"},{"pid":"114ca64d61d10f6ff12f7d2a6151bbf01b532696","tid":2241371,"uid":94484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac3c8cc0686093f22afb223cb94d5c08647fadd2","tid":2241371,"uid":47462,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"支那自己整個病毒攬炒全球仲玩死埋自己經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:52:28.000Z","msg":"食草可以食一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9b43eb3d874458d830de390016874cafe22fd2","tid":2241371,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ac386d103588cb4379d0c140c61981079a90833","tid":2241371,"uid":137159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"我睇過依條友啲片，早排話三四皮人仔去做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔計三四皮可以做乜，我假設佢目標係搵二千人仔一個月，一年二萬四，即係佢生意年回報要超過五成，賣白粉就有可能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"4，5000都做到黨主席啦"},{"pid":"e193f30b43a5c60cbf88503e23785f8f3c30340d","tid":22