觀音土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:58:19.000Z","msg":"以為 觀音土 = 香爐灰<br />\n原來「是一種含鋁的矽酸鹽礦物」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">觀音土在大飢荒時期曾被飢民當成食物充飢，吃下暫時解除飢餓感。崇禎三年（1630年）陝西大飢，陝西巡按馬懋才在《備陳大飢疏》說陝西人民只能吃觀音土填飽肚子。中華人民共和國1960年代三年大飢荒期間也有不少人吃觀音土。\n\n但觀音土並非有機食物，含大量氧化鋁，不能被人體消化吸收，儘管吃了不會餓肚子，少量吃不致命，但由於毫無營養成份，吃久了人還是會死於營養不良。此外，吃了觀音土有會腹脹、手足浮腫、便秘等症狀。因為胃部的填充對飢餓感的減除只起到一小部分的作用，曾出現過大量食用觀音土致死的案例。</code></pre><br />\n~Wikipedia"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"吃土大會~!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=444253982888255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D444253982888255&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=9741df4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=444253982888255</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3236be9c893d4953236b4213088ac57992d6ca3a","tid":2241371,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"娼盛繁榮"},{"pid":"5f87b86f0ad0681dd7f47f792f214ae9679a0baa","tid":2241371,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac3c8cc0686093f22afb223cb94d5c08647fadd2","tid":2241371,"uid":47462,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"支那自己整個病毒攬炒全球仲玩死埋自己經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"黨計劃一部分：死6億低下階層＝人均GDP go go go<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3afaa2d676387dfead20e1350b462d51eb1a65","tid":2241371,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f4beb501cee5a29508460c92f3c9c349a3c6b58","tid":2241371,"uid":11148,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:46:33